Achievements.Name: Power of Human Ingenuity
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on hard difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Great Shot
Achievements.Description: Destroy all Sensors in the game.

Achievements.Name: Easy Logistics
Achievements.Description: Earn $75,000 total cash in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Infinity Plus One
Achievements.Description: Clear the landing zone while firing from the gunship at Fort Monus.

Achievements.Name: Ultimate Zephyr
Achievements.Description: Purchase all 4 of the Zephyr EX parts in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Amplified Warrior
Achievements.Description: Equip a Mark III battle skill in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: Wicked Shot
Achievements.Description: Break all body parts on a single opponent in the single player campaign.

Achievements.Name: E.D.G.E. Master
Achievements.Description: Kill 50 enemies while in E.D.G.E. mode.

Achievements.Name: Diversity Rocks
Achievements.Description: Win a multiplayer match of all 4 types.

Achievements.Name: Around the World
Achievements.Description: Win a multiplayer match on every level.

Achievements.Name: Lead by Example
Achievements.Description: Get the top score in Team Deathmatch.

Achievements.Name: Team Player
Achievements.Description: Accumulate a total score of 10,000 while playing Domination and Supremacy.

Achievements.Name: Petals of Edelweiss
Achievements.Description: Defeat a player who has the Petals of Edelweiss achievement over Xbox LIVE.
